{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-row-to-control-spacing","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi `grid-row` za kontrolu prostora","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete učiniti da ćelije mreže pokrivaju više redova, baš kao što to možete uraditi sa kolonama. Specifikujete ravne linije koje želite da ćelija mreže počinje i završava koristeći atribut <code>grid-row</code> na ćeliji mreže.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a90373638fddaf9a66b5d39","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Neka element sa klasom <code>item5</code> uzme posled dva reda.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/c9WBLU4","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301137,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-row-to-control-spacing"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n    grid-column: 2 / 4;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>item5</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>grid-row</code>.</p>","testString":"const styleElement = document.querySelector('style:not(.fcc-hide-header)');\r\nassert.match(\r\n  __helpers.removeWhiteSpace(styleElement.textContent),\r\n  /\\.item5{.*grid-row:.*}/g\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>item5</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>grid-row</code>, što uzrokuje da uzme poslednje dve redove mreže.</p>","testString":"const itemFive = document.querySelector('.item5');\r\nconst rowStart = getComputedStyle(itemFive).gridRowStart;\r\nconst rowEnd = getComputedStyle(itemFive).gridRowEnd;\r\nconst result = rowStart.toString() + rowEnd.toString();\r\nconst correctResults = [\r\n  '24',\r\n  '2-1',\r\n  '2span 2',\r\n  '2span2',\r\n  'span 2-1',\r\n  '-12',\r\n  'span 2span 2',\r\n  'span 2auto',\r\n  'autospan 2'\r\n];\r\nassert.include(correctResults, result);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"use-grid-row-to-control-spacing","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-an-item-horizontally-using-justify-self","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-column-to-control-spacing","id":"5a90373638fddaf9a66b5d39","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"file